Package: pr.helpers
Title: Helpers for Pull and Merge Request Git Workflows
Version: 0.0.0.9013
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "David", "Morrison",
      email = "2474437+d-morrison@users.noreply.github.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Provides helper functions for common pull request and merge request
    workflows from a local Git repository. Includes utilities for creating and
    switching branches, fetching requests by number, generating request URLs, and
    syncing with the default branch across GitHub and GitLab remotes.
